<p>On the other hand, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/virosh-wedding-vijay-deverakonda-and-rashmika-mandanna-indulge-in-fun-cricket-match-before-tying-the-knot-1401022">Rashmika Mandanna</a> completed her schooling at Coorg Public School in Kodagu. After finishing school, she graduated from Bengaluru&rsquo;s MS Ramaiah College of Arts, Science, and Commerce. Rashmika also holds a bachelor&rsquo;s degree, but not in one major; she has a triple major in Psychology, Journalism, and English Literature.</p>

<p>While both actors are well educated, Rashmika holds a slight edge with qualifications in three subjects. Now, both the actors are dominating the big screens with their films.</p>

