<p><strong>Kamal Haasan takes a dig at film censoring</strong></p>

<p>While speaking at Women&rsquo;s Christian College&rsquo;s Festeve &rsquo;26 in Chennai, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/how-does-sivakarthikeyans-virumaandi-look-in-seyon-link-back-to-kamal-haasan-heres-what-we-know-1400821">Kamal Haasan</a> screened his film Lead on Gandhi, which focuses on Mahatma Gandhi. As the chief guest of the event, the actor was watching the documentary along with the students when the screen suddenly froze due to a technical glitch.</p>

