<p>Nivin Pauly was last seen in the lead role in Baby Girl, directed by Arun Varma. The film follows the story of Sanal Mathew, a medical attendant who comes under suspicion after a baby goes missing from the hospital where he works. As the seemingly innocent man faces mounting pressure, he appears to steer the police investigation in unexpected directions, creating an enigma around himself.</p>

