<h3><strong>Bhagyashree lauds Prabhas&rsquo; humble nature</strong></h3>

<p>Back in 2022, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/inside-prabhas-rs-60-crore-luxurious-house-in-hyderabad-see-pics-1377124">Prabhas</a> worked with senior actress <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/exclusives/exclusive-bhagyashree-talks-about-losing-self-belief-and-battling-depression-i-started-questioning-myself-1272616">Bhagyashree</a> in the movie Radhe Shyam. Since the Maine Pyar Kiya actress was returning to Telugu cinema after a significant amount of time, she was sceptical of Prabhas&rsquo;s behaviour towards her. While talking to TFPC, the actress revealed that her first scene, after a very long time in Telugu cinema, was with Prabhas.</p>

<p>So, when she walked on set, she thought the pan India would maintain&nbsp;distance from her. She was nervous, assuming that the Saaho actor wouldn&rsquo;t want to rehearse if she forgot her line in Telugu. But when Prabhas approached her, she was impressed by the actor&rsquo;s humbleness.</p>

<p>The Bollywood diva recalled in the old video, &ldquo;I walk on to the set, and he says,&nbsp;&lsquo;Ma&#39;am, we&#39;re such big fans of yours. We&#39;ve been watching your movie ever since.&rdquo; Upon hearing this, the actress took a sigh of relief. Calling Prabhas a &ldquo;humble person&rdquo;, Bhagyashree stated that it was very comfortable working with him. &ldquo;He didn&#39;t have any airs on set,&rdquo; she underscored, adding that not just her, but everyone was comfortable with him.</p>

<p>The Omkaram actress further divulged, &ldquo;He&#39;s not like throwing his weight around or behaving high and mighty, nothing like that. He wishes everyone on the set.&rdquo;</p>

