	<li><strong>Cast: </strong><a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/parasakthi-ott-release-when-and-where-to-watch-sivakarthikeyan-ravi-mohans-period-action-drama-1400374">Sivakarthikeyan</a>, Ravi Mohan, Atharvaa Murali, Sreeleela, Kulappulli Leela, Prakash Belawadi, Dev Ramnath, Prithvi Rajan, Guru Somasundaram, Sandhya Mridul, Chetan, Rana Daggubati (cameo), Basil Joseph (cameo)</li>
